snippet.title: Enelia: Dawn of Madness - Story Trailer (preview)
snippet.description:
https://store.steampowered. com/app/2075630/Enelia_Dawn_of_Madness/

In a world corrupted by Madness a young druid Enelia uncovers a horrifying truth that threatens her life. To save herself and her loved ones, Enelia defies public order and embarks on a journey where she meets mysterious characters, solves mysteries and makes fateful choices.

x.com/enelia_game
